{"tid":2298954,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"奇文分享：黃之鋒周庭林朗彥被酷吏凌虐證左翼對司法系統的批判","createTime":"2020-11-24T11:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T14:33:32.000Z","uid":276028,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"280e1e1b6ef9606d5a3e4381c287cea4e5d5c1d5","tid":2298954,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/featured/wong-chow-lam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Ffeatured%2Fwong-chow-lam%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=f2a6d713\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/featured/wong-chow-lam/</a><br />\n黃之鋒、周庭、林朗彥可能被重判，是因為法官只看親共報紙，不念公義因素判案嗎？<br />\n還是有更深層原因？<br />\n左翼理論可能預知到黃之鋒、周庭、林朗彥被重判？<br />\n原來左翼眼中司法界一直是權貴的玩具，對窮人不利？<br />\n香港法院定罪率接近北韓？原因為何？<br />\n香港的名流律師或許鄙視法律面前人人平等的原則？<br />\n如何讓司法系統真正為民請命？<br />\n<br />\n網上看到的左翼文章，大家可以參考一下，然後負評。"},{"pid":"26548c6959840c378570a5c4dc82d683f77af023","tid":2298954,"uid":36901,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:50:14.000Z","msg":"解決方法<br />\n人民陪審團<br />\n傳統左翼理論係人民大於法官/高官<br />\n相信普通人判斷善惡錯對能力"},{"pid":"6e22293e777c31299e0a9e499c3beb15bfeecda7","tid":2298954,"uid":106310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"香港法院定罪率接近北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e51c01c0c5be5949c2e36e10152eba689bfd6f","tid":2298954,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"歡迎藍絲負評。"},{"pid":"e07f25a82379ba2e61dc7e625b9c418bf899b94c","tid":2298954,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"多謝負評。"},{"pid":"d3fbb2de57880db3b58f2751ecf476e1518bbe0a","tid":2298954,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy"